</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_56" id="27r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Frawn Elspeten von <expan>Wirtemb<ex>er</ex>g</expan>, burggrefin czu
                        Nüremberg </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab>Gnedige frawe, uns hat <expan>fürg<ex>elegt</ex></expan> Peter Eytenholczer,
                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan>, wie im nu in <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>m</expan> slosz czu der
            Newenstat an der Eysche <expan>aufgehalte<ex>n</ex></expan> seyn worden mitnamen czwey
            pferd, xiii mark und v lote silbers. Darümb senden wir czu <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>hochwird<ex>ikeit</ex></expan>
<expan>Conrad<ex>en</ex></expan> Molitor, <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan> und dyener, mit <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> gnaden davon
            czu reden. Und bitten ewr <expan>hoch<ex>wirdikeit</ex></expan> mit
                <expan>gancze<ex>m</ex></expan> fleisz, waz <expan>ders<ex>elb</ex></expan> Molitor
            darümb czu disem mal an ewr gnade werb von <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> wegen, daz ir
            in darynne <expan>gütlich<ex>e</ex>n</expan> verhören, im des
              <expan>gelaub<ex>e</ex>n</expan> und in auch darümb
              <expan>gnediklich<ex>e</ex>n</expan> von euch vertigen wöllet. Als etc. Das wöllen
            etc. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>sabb<ex>a</ex>to</expan> post mathei <expan>ap<ex>osto</ex>li</expan> et
                <expan>ewang<ex>elia</ex><hi rend="sup">te</hi></expan>.</ab>
</div>
<div type="similiter">
<ab>Marggrafe <expan>Fridrich<ex>e</ex>n</expan> et
                            <expan>burggrafe<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>Johan<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>cuil<ex>ibet</ex></expan>
<expan>si<ex>mi</ex>l<ex>ite</ex>r</expan>
<expan>mutat<ex>is</ex></expan> etc. <expan>mutand<ex>is</ex></expan>.</ab>
</div>
